<br>
The way I see it, the stat drinks are only of benefit to people who are willing to force-consume to preserve the stat drink.   The cost and time of making the drinks is so high that it just isn't practical to consume the drinks and constantly be buying more.  The only exception I would see to this would be Kaladin Constitutional, which can be held in reserve as a resist item (same with holy cakes). <p><br>Azhrei Hiever d'Phlith, 56th Enforcer of Innoruuk's Word
